measurements.description: Two full flat flowers on one staked 8.5-cm inflorescence; sepals and petals pink-lavender, petals margins ruffled; lip closed over column, ruffled margin, pink-lavender, dark magenta distally, picotee, yellow throat, magenta veins; column white, anther cap white; substance medium; texture matte, lip velvety.
